# ============================================
# ENTERPRISE EMAIL CONFIGURATION
# ============================================
# For production/enterprise use, choose ONE of the following:
# See ENTERPRISE_EMAIL_SETUP.md for detailed instructions

# ============================================
# OPTION 1: SendGrid (RECOMMENDED - Easiest Enterprise Solution)
# ============================================
# 1. Sign up at https://signup.sendgrid.com/ (Free: 100 emails/day)
# 2. Create API Key in Settings → API Keys
# 3. Verify sender email in Settings → Sender Authentication
# 4. Add credentials below:
